  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK362">
<l>vēṇṭuṅkāl vēṇṭum piṟavāmai maṟṟatu </l>
<l>vēṇṭāmai vēṇṭa varum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If anything be desired, freedom from births should be desired; that (freedom from births) will be attained by desiring to be without desire.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
